{"view":"article","slug":"bicube","category":"Non-WCA","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Non-WCA","title":{"en":"BiCube Tutorial (Bandaged Cube)"},"content":{"en":"<p><img alt=\"H:\\QQ\\634639484\\Image\\C2C\\4A446E1AE574E6953FA115516815EE31.jpg\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image1.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">  <strong>BiCube Tutorial (Bandaged Cube)</strong></p><p><strong>捆绑魔方教程</strong></p><p>Yujian Song（宋雨键）</p><p><strong>捆绑方式</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>转动规定</strong></p><p>朝向黄顶蓝前，与三阶转动规定一致。</p><p><strong>复原2×2×3的红白绿橙块</strong></p><p>BiCube的角块基本都与棱块捆绑在一起，复原时的限制很多。这一步的大致思路是在最大的捆绑棱白绿棱两侧归位捆绑角白红绿和白绿橙。归位过程类似<a href=\"/tutorial/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>连接态的入槽，但会因捆绑太多受到限制。如何避开捆绑顺利入槽需要反复思考，但这里的难度并不算大，而且处理方式灵活多变，故不给出公式化的作法。</p><p><strong>摆正白蓝棱</strong></p><p>就是转下<strong>U</strong>和<strong>F</strong>摆正白蓝棱。</p><p><strong>归位黄蓝红角块</strong></p><p>这是唯一没有被捆绑住的角块。先将角块拿到顶层，如果还没有翻正，转动U层使其处在</p><p>UBR位置，做公式<strong>R' F R F'</strong>即可翻正，再将其转到正确位置。</p><p><strong>复原剩下的捆绑角</strong></p><p>此时BiCube只剩下5个捆绑角需要复原，处理方法是拆成三循环进行复原。</p><p>以下是这5个捆绑角构成的三循环公式，两个公式一组，互为逆序。其中前八个公式是用转换机推出来的基础三循环，但它们看上去并没有转换机的形式，可以仔细思考其中的原因。后十二个公式为由两个基础三循环叠加而成（其中最后两个有消步）。使用时完全可以只理解前八个公式的原理。而对于三循环以外的情况（五循环和两对换），总可以拆成两个三循环处理。</p><p><strong>基础三循环</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image7.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'\">U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' F' U L' U' L F U'\">R U R' F' U L' U' L F U'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 L F' L' F U' R' F R F' U'\">U2 L F' L' F U' R' F R F' U'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U F R' F' R U F' L F L' U2\">U F R' F' R U F' L F L' U2</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image9.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image10.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image11.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'\">R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R'\">R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'\">F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'\">F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>叠加三循环</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image12.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image13.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image14.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F' R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'\">F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F' R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R' F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'\">R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R' F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F' U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'\">F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F' U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' F' U L' U' L F U' F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'\">R U R' F' U L' U' L F U' F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image16.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image17.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image18.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image19.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R' U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'\">R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R' U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R'\">R U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U F' L' U L U' F R U' R' F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'\">U F' L' U L U' F R U' R' F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F' R U R' F' U L' U' L F U'\">F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F' R U R' F' U L' U' L F U'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image20.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image21.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image22.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/bicube/en/image23.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F' R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R'\">F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F' R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R' F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'\">R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R' F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' R' F' U L' U' L F U'\">R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' R' F' U L' U' L F U'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U F' L' U L U' F R F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'\">U F' L' U L U' F R F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>至此，整个魔方全部复原。</p>"},"algs":["U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'","R U R' F' U L' U' L F U'","U2 L F' L' F U' R' F R F' U'","U F R' F' R U F' L F L' U2","R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'","R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R'","F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'","F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'","F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F' R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R'","R U2 L' U' L F U' R U R' F' U' R' F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F'","F R U F' L' U L U' F R U' R2 F' U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'","R U R' F' U L' U' L F U' F R2 U R' F' U L' U' L F U' R' F'","R U F R U' R' U F' L' U L U2 R' U F' L' U L U' F R U' R'","R U R'